# 6. Proposed Solution

FitVerse AI proposes a modular AI-powered platform consisting of multiple interconnected intelligent systems.

The platform will include:

## Nutrition Intelligence

- AI Food Recognition
- Portion Size Estimation
- Automatic Calorie Calculation
- Macronutrient Tracking
- Micronutrient Analysis
- Meal Logging

---

## Workout Intelligence

- Personalized Workout Generation
- Progressive Overload
- Adaptive Training Plans
- Recovery Monitoring

---

## AI Trainer

Using computer vision and pose estimation, the AI Trainer will:

- Detect exercises
- Count repetitions
- Evaluate posture
- Provide real-time voice feedback
- Identify incorrect form
- Suggest corrections
- Reduce injury risk

Example voice feedback:

> "Keep your back neutral."

> "Brace your core."

> "Drive through your heels."

> "Slow down the lowering phase."

---

## AI Coach

An intelligent conversational assistant capable of:

- Answering nutrition questions
- Explaining exercises
- Generating meal plans
- Motivating users
- Providing recovery advice
- Analyzing user progress

---

## Progress Analytics

Automatically monitor:

- Weight
- Calories
- Protein
- Workout consistency
- Sleep
- Hydration
- Body measurements

Generate weekly and monthly reports.

